  "texts": [
    "Researchers have developed AI systems that recommend low-sodium alternatives or nutritionally dense ingredients for individuals with specific health challenges, such as hypertension or diabetes (Zadeh 2024).",
    "Studies indicate that personalized dietary recommendations that integrate flavor preferences tend to improve adherence to nutritional guidelines and increase overall satisfaction with meal choices (Ensaff 2021).",
    "This approach not only enhances compliance but also fosters a more enjoyable eating experience.",
    "Although current gustatory AI models have greatly enhanced flavor profiling and prediction, many still treat taste responses as uniform across different groups.",
    "This approach neglects the significant variability in taste perception due to genetic differences, metabolic conditions, and cultural dietary practices."
  ],
